summary:
I set-up the first Yang Sheng Clinic in Dumaguete City together with Dr. Wally back in 2000. After we moved to Laos I started a clinic in Vientiane. Here I treated over 300 patients. Now we have moved to the The Hague area in Holland and completed the registration. I can receive patients at my clinic in the Arnicalaan or organize home visits.

Specialties: Acupuncture
Traditional Chinese Medicine
Cross Cultural Training
